line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Observing the Lord’s Supper
is an act of worship that means identifying with Jesus Christ crucified and
committing ourselves to his values and purposes.  &lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>WHENCE DENOMINATIONS?</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/whence-denominations/</link><pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/whence-denominations/</guid><description>&lt;style>
