&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in'>&lt;span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Baptism
is for interpersonal identification with Christ. In consequence of identity
with him, God gives whatever the situation calls for: forgiveness of sins, gift
of the Spirit, membership in the body of Christ.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>BAPTISM: MEANING</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/baptism-meaning/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/baptism-meaning/</guid><description>&lt;style>
