style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>God’s
normal operation with people is through the Word, through other people (the
church), and by the sheer relationship itself.  &lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>EVOLUTION</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/evolution/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/evolution/</guid><description>&lt;style>
