after the fall than it was &lt;u>before the fall&lt;/u> &lt;u>in a biologically
inheritable sense&lt;/u>.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>NEW TESTAMENT CANON</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/new-testament-canon/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/new-testament-canon/</guid><description>&lt;style>
