&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in'>&lt;span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Science
deals with recurrent natural processes in the present.  Consequently, science (hard
science) does not, strictly speaking, deal with history, the supernatural, or
the metaphysical.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>SUPPORT OF THE MINISTRY</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/support-of-the-ministry/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/support-of-the-ministry/</guid><description>&lt;style>
