be important enough that God himself in the person of the Son was willing to endure
it in the extreme.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>THE TRUTHFULNESS OF CHRISTIANITY</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/the-truthfulness-of-christianity/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/the-truthfulness-of-christianity/</guid><description>&lt;style>
