&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in'>&lt;span
style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Truth
is reality in contrast to perception of reality, conception about reality,
words about reality, and the interpretation of words about reality. It is the
objective (the way it is) in contrast to the subjective (the way it seems to a
beholder).&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>WHENCE DENOMINATIONS? Dear ____,</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/whence-denominations-dear-____/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/whence-denominations-dear-____/</guid><description>&lt;style>
