&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'>&lt;span style='color:black'>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:6.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:
.5in'>&lt;span style='color:black'>Several days ago you asked why there are so
many denominations, sects, and cults in “Christendom.” Since then, I have had
the issue on my mind a lot; here are some points that describe the situation as
I see it.&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>WHY EVERYONE SINS</title><link>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/why-everyone-sins/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/essays/topics/notion-in-a-nutshell/why-everyone-sins/</guid><description>&lt;style>
