&lt;div class="word-content">
&lt;p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'>&lt;b>&lt;span
style='font-size:14.0pt'>WHY EVERYONE SINS&lt;/span>&lt;/b>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'>&lt;b>&lt;span
style='font-size:16.0pt'>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/b>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in'>People sin
because of &lt;u>evil influence&lt;/u> that appeals to &lt;u>pervertible drives&lt;/u> (all
of which can be appropriately fulfilled) and each person’s &lt;u>viewpoint of
consciousness&lt;/u> (pervertible into self-centeredness).&lt;/p>
&lt;p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify'>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>
